-- Author Gewirtz Says Government Has Right to Records (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-06-07T12:53:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-07/author-gewirtz-says-government-has-right-to-records-audio-.html
David Gewirtz, director of the U.S. 
Strategic Perspective Institute and author of "Where Have All 
The Emails Gone?", discusses the National Security Agency 
collecting telephone records of millions of U.S. Verizon 
Communications Inc. customers. Gewirtz talks with Bloomberg's 
Pimm Fox and  Carol Massar  on Bloomberg Radio's "Taking Stock."    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 08:36
 